reviewText: Another GREAT installment by Coach Don Cherry, with more hits, bloopers, goals, saves and the odd 'tussle'. You'll enjoy his Coach's Corner highlights and video replays of great hockey from the 2009 season. Highly recommended.
A great disc; Grapes never disappoints.

This is a series of CDs of some of Don Cherry' s colorful announcing of hockey games.  For the hockey enthusiast,  this is a great gift and will give hours and hours of sometimes hilarious entertainment!
I gave this to my husband for Christmas and he loved it.
I have all the Don Cherry's and this one is the same in a long line of greatness. Great highlights every year and the coaches corner is always fun to watch...what a beauty, cant wait for 25.

Great as usual.  I get the new Rock 'em Sock 'em every year.  I was, however, expecting more on the glorious return of the Jets.  There's not even a mention.  So bizarre.  I figured showing the opening night ceremony and a quick montage would be appropriate... oh well
